HEADWORD: Townhall
<hw>Town"hall`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A public hall or
building, belonging to a town, where the public offices are established,
the town council meets, the people assemble in town meeting,
etc.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

